DeÔ¨Ånition 1: Given two disjoint sets, S = {1, 2, ¬∑ ¬∑ ¬∑ , S} of

the source nodes, and K = {1, 2, ¬∑ ¬∑ ¬∑ , K} of the sub-channels,

a many-to-many matching Œ® is a mapping from the set S ‚à™ K

